section.para:
An example:[sales]
exten => _12X.,1,NoOp{12X}
exten => 12345,1,NoOp(12345}
exten => _1234.,1,NoOp{1234.}

Let's try adding the extension "_." to our previous dialplan
      example:[sales]
exten => _12X.,1,NoOp{12X}
exten => 12345,1,NoOp(12345}
exten => _1234.,1,NoOp{1234.}

exten => _.,1,NoOp{Bingo}

This is why it is preferable to use "_X." as the
      wildcard pattern (if we use a wildcard pattern at all!). The following
      dialplan example is processed identically in Asterisk 1.2 and
      1.4:[sales]
exten => _12X.,1,NoOp{12X}
exten => 12345,1,NoOp(12345}
exten => _1234.,1,NoOp{1234.}

exten => _X.,1,NoOp{Bingo}
